<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Greg Alvo — LinkedIn Performance Dashboard</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Figtree:wght@300;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@24,300,0,0" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --og-midnight: #17132F;
  --og-dark-indigo: #2E2A47;
  --og-green: #009A50;
  --og-groovy-green: #00FF85;
  --og-intense-cyan: #00FAFF;
  --og-laser-lemon: #EAFF00;
  --og-white: #FFFFFF;
  --og-off-white: #F5F5F5;
  --og-font: 'Figtree', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;

  /* Semantic tokens */
  --bg: var(--og-midnight);
  --surface: var(--og-white);
  --surface2: #F5F5F5;
  --border: transparent;
  --text: var(--og-midnight);
  --text-dim: var(--og-midnight);
  --text-muted: var(--og-midnight);
  --text-on-dark: var(--og-white);
  --accent: var(--og-green);
  --accent-bright: var(--og-groovy-green);
  --accent-glow: rgba(0,154,80,0.08);

  /* Chart system colors (OG spec) */
  --chart-1: #00FF85;
  --chart-2: #009A50;
  --chart-3: #00FAFF;
  --chart-4: #0080B0;
  --chart-5: #004F8C;
  --chart-6: #EAFF00;
  --chart-7: #FF8C00;
  --chart-8: #D46AFF;
  --chart-9: #7821F5;

  /* Semantic chart colors */
  --green-up: var(--og-green);
  --green-dim: rgba(0,154,80,0.1);
  --red: #C7254E;
  --red-dim: rgba(199,37,78,0.08);
  --blue: #0080B0;
  --blue-dim: rgba(0,128,176,0.08);
  --yellow: #B08900;
  --yellow-dim: rgba(176,137,0,0.08);
  --purple: #7821F5;
  --purple-dim: rgba(120,33,245,0.08);

  --radius: 12px;
  --radius-sm: 8px;
}

* { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }

body {
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text-on-dark);
  font-family: var(--og-font);
  font-weight: 500;
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 1.5;
  min-height: 100vh;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
}

.material-symbols-outlined {
  font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0, 'wght' 300, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 24;
  vertical-align: middle;
}

.container {
  max-width: 1280px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 40px 32px 80px;
}

/* ── HEADER (dark panel per OG brand) ── */
.header {
  background: transparent;
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 40px 0 36px;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
/* Brand blob shape */
.header::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  width: 280px;
  height: 280px;
  right: -40px;
  top: -80px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #009A50, #00FF85, #00FAFF);
  border-radius: 60% 40% 70% 30% / 50% 60% 40% 50%;
  opacity: 0.25;
}
.header::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  width: 180px;
  height: 180px;
  right: 60px;
  bottom: -60px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00FF85, #71ACFF, #7821F5);
  border-radius: 40% 60% 30% 70% / 60% 40% 50% 50%;
  opacity: 0.15;
}
.header h1 {
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 40px;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  line-height: 1.1;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  color: var(--og-white);
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}
.header h1 span {
  color: var(--og-groovy-green);
}
.header p {
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 500;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}
.header p strong {
  color: var(--og-white);
  font-weight: 700;
}

/* ── BIG STAT CARDS ── */
.stats-row {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}
.stat-card {
  background: var(--og-white);
  border: none;
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 24px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
}
.stat-card::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
  height: 3px;
}
.stat-card:nth-child(1)::before { background: var(--og-green); }
.stat-card:nth-child(2)::before { background: var(--chart-3); }
.stat-card:nth-child(3)::before { background: var(--chart-4); }
.stat-card:nth-child(4)::before { background: var(--chart-7); }
.stat-label {
  font-size: 11px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  color: var(--og-midnight);
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  opacity: 0.6;
}
.stat-value {
  font-size: 40px;
  font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 4px;
  color: var(--og-midnight);
}
.stat-sub {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--og-midnight);
  opacity: 0.6;
}

/* ── SECTION HEADERS ── */
.section-header {
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 1.75rem;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  margin-top: 48px;
  padding-bottom: 12px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  color: var(--og-white);
}
.section-header span {
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
  font-size: 13px;
  margin-left: 12px;
  font-weight: 500;
}

/* ── INSIGHT GRID ── */
.insight-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  gap: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}
.insight-card {
  background: var(--og-white);
  border: none;
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 24px;
  transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
}
.insight-card:hover {
  box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
}
.insight-card h3 {
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  color: var(--og-midnight);
}
.badge {
  font-size: 10px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  padding: 3px 8px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  font-weight: 700;
}
.badge-up { background: var(--green-dim); color: var(--og-green); }
.badge-down { background: var(--red-dim); color: var(--red); }
.badge-info { background: var(--blue-dim); color: var(--blue); }

/* ── HORIZONTAL BAR CHARTS ── */
.hbar-group { margin-bottom: 8px; }
.hbar-row {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
  cursor: default;
}
.hbar-row:hover .hbar-fill { filter: brightness(1.1); }
.hbar-label {
  width: 140px;
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text-dim);
  flex-shrink: 0;
  text-align: right;
  padding-right: 16px;
  font-weight: 500;
}
.hbar-track {
  flex: 1;
  height: 32px;
  background: #EEEEEE;
  border-radius: 6px;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.hbar-fill {
  height: 100%;
  border-radius: 6px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: flex-end;
  padding-right: 10px;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 700;
  transition: width 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  min-width: 50px;
  color: var(--og-midnight);
}
.hbar-meta {
  width: 70px;
  text-align: right;
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  padding-left: 10px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  font-weight: 500;
}

/* ── DOT STRIP ── */
.dot-strip {
  display: flex;
  align-items: end;
  gap: 2px;
  height: 110px;
  padding: 16px 0;
  background: var(--og-white);
  border: none;
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 20px 16px 16px;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
}
.dot-strip-bar {
  flex: 1;
  border-radius: 2px 2px 0 0;
  min-height: 2px;
  transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
  cursor: pointer;
  position: relative;
}
.dot-strip-bar:hover { transform: scaleX(1.5); }
.dot-strip-bar.top { opacity: 1; background: var(--og-green); }
.dot-strip-bar.mid { opacity: 0.7; background: var(--chart-4); }
.dot-strip-bar.low { opacity: 0.6; background: var(--og-dark-indigo); }

/* ── TOOLTIP ── */
.tooltip {
  position: fixed;
  background: var(--og-midnight);
  border: 1px solid var(--og-dark-indigo);
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  padding: 14px 18px;
  font-size: 12px;
  max-width: 340px;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 1000;
  box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(23,19,47,0.35);
  display: none;
  line-height: 1.5;
  color: var(--og-white);
}
.tooltip .tt-eng {
  font-size: 24px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--og-groovy-green);
}
.tooltip .tt-meta {
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
  margin-top: 4px;
  font-weight: 500;
}
.tooltip .tt-content {
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  margin-top: 6px;
  font-style: italic;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  padding-top: 6px;
}

/* ── MULTIPLIER CARDS ── */
.multiplier-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 12px;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}
.mult-card {
  background: var(--og-white);
  border: none;
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 24px;
  text-align: left;
  transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
}
.mult-card:hover { box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.18); }
.mult-card .mult-takeaway {
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.35;
  color: var(--og-midnight);
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.mult-card .mult-takeaway em {
  font-style: normal;
  color: var(--og-green);
}
.mult-card .mult-bar-track {
  height: 6px;
  background: #EEEEEE;
  border-radius: 3px;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.mult-card .mult-bar-fill {
  height: 100%;
  border-radius: 3px;
  background: var(--og-green);
  transition: width 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
}
.mult-card .mult-stat {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--og-midnight);
  opacity: 0.7;
  font-weight: 500;
}

/* ── TAKEAWAY CALLOUT ── */
.takeaway {
  background: var(--og-dark-indigo);
  border-left: 3px solid var(--og-groovy-green);
  border-radius: 0 var(--radius-sm) var(--radius-sm) 0;
  padding: 14px 20px;
  margin: -2px 0 10px 0;
  font-size: 13px;
  line-height: 1.55;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
  font-weight: 500;
}
.takeaway strong { color: var(--og-white); font-weight: 700; }
.takeaway em { color: var(--og-groovy-green); font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; }

/* ── RANKED MULTIPLIER CARDS ── */
.ranked-list {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 10px;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}
.ranked-card {
  background: var(--og-white);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 20px 24px;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 36px 1fr auto;
  gap: 16px;
  align-items: start;
}
.ranked-num {
  font-size: 20px;
  padding-top: 2px;
  text-align: center;
  line-height: 1;
}
.ranked-body {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 8px;
}
.ranked-label {
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--og-midnight);
  line-height: 1.3;
}
.ranked-bar-track {
  height: 8px;
  background: #EEEEEE;
  border-radius: 4px;
  overflow: hidden;
  width: 100%;
}
.ranked-bar-fill {
  height: 100%;
  border-radius: 4px;
  background: var(--og-green);
  transition: width 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
}
.ranked-lift {
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--og-green);
  white-space: nowrap;
  padding-top: 1px;
}

/* ── STOP DOING SECTION ── */
.stop-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 12px;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}
.stop-card {
  background: var(--og-white);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 24px;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
  border-top: 3px solid var(--red);
}
.stop-card h4 {
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--og-midnight);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.stop-card p {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--og-midnight);
  opacity: 0.7;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

/* ── FORMAT COMPARISON CHART ── */
.format-chart {
  background: var(--og-white);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 28px;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}
.format-chart h3 {
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--og-midnight);
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
}
.format-row {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 140px 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 12px;
  align-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}
.format-label {
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--og-midnight);
}
.format-bar-wrap {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
}
.format-bar {
  height: 28px;
  border-radius: 6px;
  transition: width 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
}
.format-bar-pct {
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--og-midnight);
  min-width: 36px;
}
.format-legend {
  display: flex;
  gap: 24px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--og-midnight);
  opacity: 0.6;
}
.format-legend span {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
}
.format-legend-dot {
  width: 10px;
  height: 10px;
  border-radius: 3px;
  display: inline-block;
}

/* ── FORMULA BOX ── */
.formula-box {
  background: var(--og-dark-indigo);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 40px 36px 36px;
  margin: 32px 0;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.formula-box::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  width: 260px;
  height: 260px;
  right: -60px;
  bottom: -100px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #009A50, #00FF85, #00FAFF);
  border-radius: 60% 40% 70% 30% / 50% 60% 40% 50%;
  opacity: 0.12;
}
.formula-box .formula-title {
  font-size: 28px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--og-white);
  margin-bottom: 6px;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}
.formula-box .formula-title span {
  color: var(--og-groovy-green);
}
.formula-box .formula-sub {
  font-size: 15px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  max-width: 640px;
  line-height: 1.55;
}
.formula-steps {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-top: 16px;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}
.formula-step {
  background: var(--og-dark-indigo);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  padding: 14px 16px;
  text-align: center;
  flex: 1;
  min-width: 130px;
}
.formula-step .fs-num {
  font-size: 10px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  margin-bottom: 4px;
  font-weight: 700;
}
.formula-step .fs-title {
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 13px;
  margin-bottom: 2px;
  color: var(--og-groovy-green);
}
.formula-step .fs-desc {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
  font-weight: 500;
}
.formula-arrow {
  font-size: 18px;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
  padding: 0 6px;
}

/* ── POST FEED ── */
.post-feed {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 6px;
}
.post-row {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 36px 1fr auto;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 16px;
  padding: 12px 16px;
  background: var(--og-white);
  border: none;
  border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  transition: box-shadow 0.15s;
  cursor: default;
  box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  text-decoration: none;
  color: inherit;
}
.post-row:hover { box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.16); }
a.post-link { cursor: pointer; }
a.post-link:hover { box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,154,80,0.2); }
.post-rank {
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--og-midnight);
  opacity: 0.4;
  text-align: center;
}
.post-eng {
  font-size: 20px;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-align: center;
}
.post-content {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text-dim);
  overflow: hidden;
  text-overflow: ellipsis;
  white-space: nowrap;
  font-weight: 500;
}
.post-tags {
  display: flex;
  gap: 4px;
  justify-content: flex-end;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.post-tag {
  font-size: 9px;
  padding: 2px 6px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  font-weight: 700;
}

/* ── FILTER PILLS ── */
.filter-bar {
  display: flex;
  gap: 8px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.filter-pill {
  padding: 6px 14px;
  border-radius: 9999px;
  border: none;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
  font-size: 12px;
  font-family: var(--og-font);
  font-weight: 500;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.15s;
}
.filter-pill:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); color: var(--og-white); }
.filter-pill.active {
  background: var(--og-green);
  border: none;
  color: var(--og-white);
  font-weight: 700;
}

/* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .stats-row { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  .insight-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .stop-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .header h1 { font-size: 28px; }
  .formula-steps { flex-direction: column; }
  .formula-arrow { transform: rotate(90deg); }
  .container { padding: 20px 16px 60px; }
  .format-row { grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr 1fr; }
}

/* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
@keyframes fadeUp {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}
.animate-in {
  animation: fadeUp 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) forwards;
  opacity: 0;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
  <!-- Header (dark panel) -->
  <div class="header animate-in">
    <h1>Greg Alvo <span>LinkedIn Performance</span></h1>
    <p><strong>220 original posts</strong> analyzed &mdash; engagement = likes + comments + reposts</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Big Stats -->
  <div class="stats-row" id="statsRow"></div>

  <!-- The Formula (dark panel) -->
  <div class="formula-box animate-in" style="animation-delay:0.12s">
    <div class="formula-title"><span>The Formula</span></div>
    <div class="formula-sub">Based on 220 posts of data, here's the repeatable pattern for high-performing exec LinkedIn content:</div>
    <div class="formula-steps">
      <div class="formula-step">
        <div class="fs-num">Step 1</div>
        <div class="fs-title">Narrative Hook</div>
        <div class="fs-desc">"Last week..." "When I started..."</div>
      </div>
      <div class="formula-arrow">&rarr;</div>
      <div class="formula-step">
        <div class="fs-num">Step 2</div>
        <div class="fs-title">The Thing</div>
        <div class="fs-desc">Name the brand + what happened</div>
      </div>
      <div class="formula-arrow">&rarr;</div>
      <div class="formula-step">
        <div class="fs-num">Step 3</div>
        <div class="fs-title">The So-What</div>
        <div class="fs-desc">Founder POV on why it matters</div>
      </div>
